request.description:
Scan for products by EPC value(s). Supports both single EPC value (epcValue) and multiple EPC values (epcValues). You can use either field or both. Examples:

Single EPC: {"epcValue": "RFID001"}
Multiple EPCs: {"epcValues": ["RFID001", "RFID002"]}
Both: {"epcValue": "RFID001", "epcValues": ["RFID002", "RFID003"]}

Note: If both fields are provided, all unique EPC values will be scanned. Duplicates are automatically removed.

